DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Month
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"Closed and In Progress Tickets","WidgetType":"rangeselector","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"#e0e0e0","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":0,"WidgetRows":3,"WidgetColumns":48,"WidgetHeader":{"showContextInfo":false,"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"startDate":"2019/11/01","endDate":"2019/12/30","type":"year","visible":false},"showSubTitle":false,"showTitle":false},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"select	day as Week,
		0 as Billed,
		0 as PurchasedInternal,
		0 as PurchasedExternal,
		0 as Margin
from	YearDay ydy
where	year(ydy.Day) = year(getdate()) and
		ydy.Day not in (select Date from Bill)
union all
select	min(bil.Date) as Week,
		sum(elg.ValueWithoutVatIncome) as Billed,
		sum(iif(sup.Company is not null, elg.ValueWithoutVatCost, 0)) as PurchasedInternal,
		sum(iif(sup.Company is null, elg.ValueWithoutVatCost, 0)) as PurchasedExternal,
		sum(elg.ValueWithoutVatIncome - elg.ValueWithoutVatCost) as Margin
from	EstimateLog elg, Supplier sup, Bill bil
where	bil.Oid = elg.Bill and
		sup.Oid = elg.SupplierCost 
group by datepart(year, bil.Date),
        datepart(week, bil.Date)","mapping":""}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":null}]

DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Rentabilidade
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"","WidgetType":"grid","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":3,"WidgetRows":33,"WidgetColumns":48,"WidgetHeader":{"showContextInfo":false,"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"type":"year","visible":false},"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":false,"Metrics":[{"visible":true,"metricName":"# Delayed Under Development","metricFieldValue":"DelayedUnderDevelopmentJobsGrandTotal"}]},"showSubTitle":false,"showTitle":false},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"with	t as 
		(
		select	bil.Company,
				bil.Client,
                bil.Contract,
                bil.Project,
				sum(iif(bcl.RelatedCompany is not null, bil.ValueWithoutVat, 0)) as BilledInternal,
				sum(iif(bcl.RelatedCompany is null, bil.ValueWithoutVat, 0)) as BilledExternal,
				sum(bil.ValueWithoutVat) as Billed,
				max(est.ValueWithoutVatIncome) as EstimatedIncome,
				0 as EstimatedIncomeInternal,
				0 as EstimatedIncomeResources,
				0 as EstimatedIncomeThirdParty,
				0 as PurchasedInternal,
				0 as PurchasedThirdParty
		from	Bill bil,
                Estimate est,
				Client bcl
		where	est.Oid = bil.Estimate and
				bcl.Oid = bil.BillingClient and
                bil.[External] is not null and
				bil.Date between @FromDate and @ToDate
        group by bil.Company, bil.Client, bil.Contract, bil.Project, est.Oid
		union all
		select	bil.Company,
				bil.Client,
                bil.Contract,
                bil.Project,
				0 as BilledInternal,
				0 as BilledExternal,
				0 as Billed,
				0 as Estimated,
				sum(iif(eid.Type = 0 and sup.RelatedCompany is not null, iif(est.ValueWithoutVatIncome != 0, bil.ValueWithoutVat / est.ValueWithoutVatIncome, 0) * eid.ValueWithoutVatCost, 0)) as EstimatedIncomeInternal,
				sum(iif(eid.Type = 2, iif(est.ValueWithoutVatIncome != 0, bil.ValueWithoutVat / est.ValueWithoutVatIncome, 0) * eid.ValueWithoutVatCost, 0)) as EstimatedIncomeResources,
				sum(iif(eid.Type = 0 and sup.RelatedCompany is null, iif(est.ValueWithoutVatIncome != 0, bil.ValueWithoutVat / est.ValueWithoutVatIncome, 0) * eid.ValueWithoutVatCost, 0)) as EstimatedIncomeThirdParty,
				0 as PurchasedInternal,
				0 as PurchasedThirdParty
		from	Bill bil,
				Estimate est,
				EstimateItem eit,
				EstimateItemDetail eid left join Supplier sup on sup.Oid = eid.SupplierCost
		where	est.Oid = bil.Estimate and
				eit.Estimate = est.Oid and
				eid.EstimateItem = eit.Oid and
				bil.[External] is not null and
				bil.Date between @FromDate and @ToDate
        group by bil.Company, bil.Client, bil.Contract, bil.Project
		union all
		select	est.Company,
				est.Client,
                est.Contract,
                est.Project,
				0 as BilledInternal,
				0 as BilledExternal,
				0 as Billed,
				0 as Estimated,
				0 as EstimatedIncomeInternal,
				0 as EstimatedIncomeResources,
				0 as EstimatedIncomeThirdParty,
				sum(iif(sup.RelatedCompany is not null, por.ValueWithoutVat, 0)) as PurchasedInternal,
				sum(iif(sup.RelatedCompany is null, por.ValueWithoutVat, 0)) as PurchasedThirdParty
		from	PurchaseOrder por,
				Estimate est,
				Supplier sup
		where	est.Oid in (
					select	bil.Estimate 
					from	Bill bil 
					where	bil.[External] is not null and
							bil.Date between @FromDate and @ToDate
				) and
				por.Estimate = est.Oid and
				sup.Oid = por.Supplier
        group by est.Company, est.Client, est.Contract, est.Project
		)
select	com.Name as Company,
		com.Oid as CompanyId,
		com.HasImage as CompanyHasImage,
		'Project' as WorkOrderType,
		prj.Oid as WorkOrderId,
		prj.Number as WorkOrderNumber,
		prj.Name as WorkOrder,
		stg.Name as Stage,
        isnull(stg.Color, wst.Color) as StageColor,
		cli.Name as Client,
        cli.Oid as ClientId,
        cli.HasImage as ClientHasImage,
		sum(t.BilledInternal) as BilledInternal,
		sum(t.BilledExternal) as BilledExternal,
		sum(t.Billed) as Billed,
        sum(t.EstimatedIncome - (t.BilledInternal + t.BilledExternal)) as Unbilled,
		sum(t.EstimatedIncomeInternal) as EstimatedIncomeInternal,
		sum(t.EstimatedIncomeThirdParty) as EstimatedIncomeThirdParty,
		sum(t.EstimatedIncomeResources) as EstimatedIncomeResources,
		sum(t.PurchasedInternal) as PurchasedInternal,
		sum(t.PurchasedThirdParty) as PurchasedThirdParty,
		iif(sum(t.Billed) != 0, sum(t.Billed - t.EstimatedIncomeThirdParty) / sum(t.Billed), 0) as Margin,
		iif(sum(t.EstimatedIncome) != 0, sum(t.Billed) / sum(t.EstimatedIncome), 0) as BilledPercentage
from	t, Project prj, WorkflowState stg, WorkflowStateType wst, Company com, CommercialClient cli
where	prj.Oid = t.Project and
		stg.Oid = prj.WorkflowState and
        wst.Oid = stg.WorkflowStateType and
		com.Oid = t.Company and
		cli.Oid = t.Client 
group by com.Name, com.Oid, com.HasImage, prj.Oid, prj.Number, prj.Name, stg.Name, stg.Color, wst.Color, cli.Name, cli.Oid, cli.HasImage
union all
select	com.Name as Company,
		com.Oid as CompanyId,
		com.HasImage as CompanyHasImage,
		'Contract' as WorkOrderType,
		cnt.Oid as WorkOrderId,
		cnt.Number as WorkOrderNmuber,
		cnt.Name as WorkOrder,
		stg.Name as Stage,
		isnull(stg.Color, wst.Color) as StageColor,
		cli.Name as Client,
        cli.Oid as ClientId,
        cli.HasImage as ClientHasImage,
		sum(t.BilledInternal) as BilledInternal,
		sum(t.BilledExternal) as BilledExternal,
		sum(t.Billed) as Billed,
        sum(t.EstimatedIncome - t.Billed) as Unbilled,
		sum(t.EstimatedIncomeInternal) as EstimatedIncomeInternal,
		sum(t.EstimatedIncomeThirdParty) as EstimatedIncomeThirdParty,
		sum(t.EstimatedIncomeResources) as EstimatedIncomeResources,
		sum(t.PurchasedInternal) as PurchasedInternal,
		sum(t.PurchasedThirdParty) as PurchasedThirdParty,
		iif(sum(t.Billed) != 0, sum(t.Billed - t.EstimatedIncomeThirdParty) / sum(t.Billed), 0) as Margin,
		iif(sum(t.EstimatedIncome) != 0, sum(t.Billed) / sum(t.EstimatedIncome), 0) as BilledPercentage
from	t, Contract cnt, WorkflowState stg, WorkflowStateType wst, Company com, CommercialClient cli
where	cnt.Oid = t.Contract and
		stg.Oid = cnt.WorkflowState and
        wst.Oid = stg.WorkflowStateType and
        t.Project is null and
		com.Oid = t.Company and
		cli.Oid = t.Client 
group by com.Name, com.Oid, com.HasImage, cnt.Oid, cnt.Number, cnt.Name, stg.Name, stg.Color, wst.Color, cli.Name, cli.Oid, cli.HasImage
","mapping":""}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"RequiredFilters":["startDate","endDate"]}}]
